<p><span data-contrast="auto">이번</span> <span data-contrast="auto">수상은</span> <span data-contrast="auto">혁신</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">최첨단</span> <span data-contrast="auto">기술</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">우수한</span> <span data-contrast="auto">고객서비스</span> <span data-contrast="auto">제공을</span> <span data-contrast="auto">향한</span><span data-contrast="auto"> ATFX</span><span data-contrast="auto">의</span> <span data-contrast="auto">전념이</span> <span data-contrast="auto">반영되었다고</span> <span data-contrast="auto">할</span> <span data-contrast="auto">수</span> <span data-contrast="auto">있습니다</span><span data-contrast="auto">. ATFX</span><span data-contrast="auto">는</span> <span data-contrast="auto">전문적인</span> <span data-contrast="auto">트레이딩</span> <span data-contrast="auto">툴</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">경쟁력</span> <span data-contrast="auto">있는</span> <span data-contrast="auto">스프레드</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">광속</span> <span data-contrast="auto">주문집행</span> <span data-contrast="auto">속도로</span> <span data-contrast="auto">무장한</span> <span data-contrast="auto">트레이딩</span> <span data-contrast="auto">플랫폼을</span> <span data-contrast="auto">꾸준히</span> <span data-contrast="auto">개선해</span> <span data-contrast="auto">왔으며</span><span data-contrast="auto">, </span><span data-contrast="auto">이를</span> <span data-contrast="auto">통해</span> <span data-contrast="auto">트레이더</span> <span data-contrast="auto">분들이</span> <span data-contrast="auto">최고의</span> <span data-contrast="auto">트레이딩</span> <span data-contrast="auto">환경을</span> <span data-contrast="auto">누리실</span> <span data-contrast="auto">수</span> <span data-contrast="auto">있게끔</span> <span data-contrast="auto">하고</span> <span data-contrast="auto">있습니다</span><span data-contrast="auto">. </span><span data-contrast="auto">이</span> <span data-contrast="auto">같은</span> <span dat