		<title>ATFX, ‘2025 갈라 저녁 만찬’ 연례행사로 미래의 빛 밝혀</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/ko/company-news/atfx-illuminates-future-2025-annual-gala-dinner</link>
		
